 French Pharmacovigilance  Database." J Clin Psychopharmacol  (2015):[38] Shakoor M, Ayub S, Ahad A, Ayub Z "Transient serotonin syndrome caused by concurrent use of tramadol and selective serotonin reuptake inhibitor." Am J Case Rep 15 (2014):  562-4[39] Larson KJ, Wittwer ED, Nicholson WT, Weingarten TN, Price DL, Sprung J "Myoclonus in patient on fluoxetine after receiving fentanyl and low-dose methylene blue during sentinel lymph node biopsy." J Clin Anesth 27 (2015):  247-51[40] US Food and Drug Administration (FDA) "FDA Drug Safety Communication: FDA warns about several safety issues with opioid pain medicines; requires label changes.  https://www.fda.gov/downloads/Drugs/DrugSafety/UCM491302.pdf"   (2018):', 1767369485);
